{
  "stem": "14002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At 12 o'clock, they gave us a soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The soup was-- I think it was-- it was cooked-- cooked cucumber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The same thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was hot like fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The sun was burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they told you just to eat it up, without a spoon, by the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Didn't give you no spoon or anything, just from the plate itself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You didn't finish it, out it goes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Again, running the same quarry, down, over again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think we started off-- we started off that time and became-- I think we started off, from Plaszow, about 300-- over 300 people in there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "After two weeks, we were about 24 left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then they took us again on a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We came to a city named Melk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's also in Austria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] [GASP]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we reached Melk, when we came down from the train, there were no SS waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the Luftwaffe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The air force-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means the air force.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very happy about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came over there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they told us that we are going to work here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What happened in Melk-- what happened in Melk was this here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were building a factory in a mountain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were building-- I think it was-- it was ball bearings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they wanted to make it in the mountain, because-- for the-- for the American and the English Air Force shouldn't be able to bomb them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next day, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My work was there, with an air hammer, to dig in the mountain the stone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, well, to make, like, a tunnel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was another crew.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
